\sum_{i=0}^n(5i-3) = \left(\sum_{i=0}^n(5i) - 3n\right)
 S = 2 + 7 + 12 + \dots + (5n - 3) = \sum_{i=1}^n (5i-3) = \left(5\sum_{i=1}^{n} i\right) - 3n. 
 \sum_{i=1}^{n} i = \frac{n(n-1)}{2}. 
